('1', '1', '0', 0x61626f6d61736e6f77, '0', '12', 0x3135, '0', 0x31, '0', '1', '0', '0', '90', 0x3932, 0x3735, '92', '85', '60', '214', 0x3732, '237', '128', '60', '128', '4', '42', '/* Code Generated */ ', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Snow Warning|100|Soundproof|10|', '', 'They appear when the snow flowers bloom. When the petals fall, they retreat to places unknown again.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('2', '1', '0', 0x61627261, '0', '14', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '25', 0x3230, 0x3135, '105', '55', '90', '75', 0x3130, '194', '128', '200', '64', '3', '42', 'if ($this->Level() >=16) return \'Kadabra\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Synchronize|100|Inner Focus|50|Magic Guard|10', '', 'Using its psychic power is such a strain on its brain that it needs to sleep for 18 hours a day.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('3', '1', '0', 0x6162736f6c, '0', '17', '0', '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '65', 0x313330, 0x3630, '75', '60', '75', '174', 0x3236, '190', '64', '30', '128', '3', '52', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Super Luck|100|Justified|50|', '', 'It appears from deep in the mountains to warn people about upcoming disasters it has sensed with its horn.', 'Mammalia', 'Carnivora', 'Canis', '', ''),
('4', '1', '0', 0x616363656c676f72, '0', '7', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '2', '80', 0x3730, 0x3430, '100', '60', '145', '173', 0x3134, '5', '128', '75', '128', '2', '32', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Hydration|100|Sticky Hold|50|Unburden|10', '', 'When its body dries out, it weakens. So it wraps a membrane around itself for protection while it spits poison.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('5', '1', '0', 0x6165726f64616374796c, '0', '6', 0x33, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '2', '80', 0x313035, 0x3635, '60', '75', '130', '202', 0x3332, '155', '128', '45', '32', '4', '62', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Rock Head|100|Pressure|50|Unnerve|10', '', 'A Pokémon that roamed the skies in the dinosaur era. Its teeth are like saw blades.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('6', '1', '0', 0x616767726f6e, '0', '9', 0x36, '0', '0', 0x33, '0', '0', '0', '70', 0x313130, 0x313830, '60', '60', '50', '205', 0x313932, '187', '64', '45', '128', '4', '72', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Sturdy|100|Rock Head|50|Heavy Metal|10', '', 'It claims an entire mountain as its own. The more wounds it has, the more it has battled, so don\'t take it lightly.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('7', '1', '0', 0x6169706f6d, '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '55', 0x3730, 0x3535, '40', '55', '85', '94', 0x36, '137', '128', '45', '128', '1', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Run Away|100|Pickup|50|Skill Link|10|', '', 'It lives high among the treetops. It can use its tail as freely and cleverly as its hands.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('8', '1', '0', 0x616c616b617a616d, '0', '14', '0', '0', '0', '0', '3', '0', '0', '55', 0x3530, 0x3435, '135', '85', '120', '186', 0x3236, '61', '128', '50', '64', '3', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Synchronize|100|Inner Focus|50|Magic Guard|10', '', 'The spoons clutched in its hands are said to have been created by its psychic powers.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('9', '1', '0', 0x616c6f6d6f6d6f6c61, '0', '11', '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '165', 0x3735, 0x3830, '40', '45', '65', '165', 0x3136, '12', '128', '75', '128', '1', '82', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Healer|100|Hydration|50|Regenerator|10', '', 'It gently holds injured and weak Pokémon in its fins. Its special membrane heals their wounds.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('10', '1', '0', 0x616c7461726961, '0', '16', 0x33, '0', '0', '0', '0', 0x32, '0', '75', 0x3730, 0x3930, '70', '105', '80', '188', 0x3132, '180', '128', '45', '128', '0', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Natural Cure|100|Cloud Nine|10', '', 'On sunny days, it flies freely through the sky and blends into the clouds. It sings in a beautiful soprano.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('11', '1', '0', 0x616d6269706f6d, '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '2', '75', 0x313030, 0x3636, '60', '66', '115', '186', 0x3130, '192', '182', '45', '128', '1', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Technician|100|Pickup|50|Skill Link|10', '', 'Split into two, the tails are so adept at handling and doing things, Ambipom rarely uses its hands.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('12', '1', '0', 0x616d6f6f6e67757373, '0', '12', 0x34, 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '114', 0x3835, 0x3730, '85', '80', '30', '162', 0x36, '23', '128', '75', '128', '2', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Effect Spore|100|Regenerator|10', '', 'It moves the caps on both arms and does a dance to lure prey. It prefers damp places.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('13', '1', '0', 0x616d706861726f73, '0', '13', '0', '0', '0', '0', '3', '0', '0', '90', 0x3735, 0x3735, '115', '90', '55', '194', 0x3332, '227', '128', '45', '128', '3', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Static|100|Plus|10', '', 'The tip of its tail shines so brightly it can be used to send sea-navigation beacons to distant foreign shores.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('14', '1', '0', 0x616e6f72697468, '0', '6', 0x37, '0', 0x31, '0', '0', '0', '0', '45', 0x3935, 0x3530, '40', '50', '75', '99', 0x36, '142', '128', '45', '32', '0', '62', 'if ($this->Level() >=40) return \'Armaldo\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Battle Armor|100|Swift Swim|10', '', 'A Pokémon ancestor that was reanimated from a fossil. It lived in the sea and hunted with claws.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('15', '1', '0', 0x6172626f6b, '0', '4', '0', '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '60', 0x3835, 0x3639, '65', '79', '80', '147', 0x3334, '225', '128', '90', '128', '2', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Intimidate|100|Shed Skin|50|Unnerve|10|', '', 'The pattern on its belly is for intimidation. It constricts foes while they are frozen in fear.', 'Reptilia', 'Squamata', 'Serpentes', '', ''),
('16', '1', '0', 0x617263616e696e65, '0', '10', '0', '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '90', 0x313130, 0x3830, '100', '80', '95', '213', 0x3832, '135', '128', '75', '64', '4', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Intimidate|100|Flash Fire|50|Justified|10', '', 'The sight of it running over 6,200 miles in a single day and night has captivated many people.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('17', '1', '0', 0x617263657573, '0', '1', '0', 0x33, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '120', 0x313230, 0x313230, '120', '120', '120', '255', 0x313732, '255', '0', '3', '255', '4', '242', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Multitype|100', '', 'It is said to have emerged from an egg in a place where there was nothing then shaped the world.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('18', '1', '0', 0x61726368656e, '0', '6', 0x33, '0', 0x31, '0', '0', '0', '0', '55', 0x313132, 0x3435, '74', '45', '70', '71', 0x36, '1', '128', '45', '32', '2', '62', 'if ($this->Level() >=37) return \'Archeops\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Defeatist|100', '', 'It was revived from an ancient fossil. Not able to fly, it lived in treetops and hopped from one branch to another.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('19', '1', '0', 0x61726368656f7073, '0', '6', 0x33, '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '75', 0x313430, 0x3635, '112', '65', '110', '177', 0x3138, '22', '128', '45', '32', '2', '62', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Defeatist|100', '', 'It runs better than it flies. It takes off into the sky by running at a speed of 25 mph.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('20', '1', '0', 0x61726961646f73, '0', '7', 0x34, '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '70', 0x3930, 0x3730, '60', '60', '40', '134', 0x3138, '207', '128', '90', '128', '1', '32', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Swarm|100|Insomnia|50|Sniper|10', '', 'It attaches silk to its prey and sets it free. Later, it tracks the silk to the prey and its friends.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('21', '1', '0', 0x61726d616c646f, '0', '6', 0x37, '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '75', 0x313235, 0x313030, '70', '80', '45', '199', 0x3336, '236', '128', '45', '32', '0', '62', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Battle Armor|100|Swift Swim|10', '', 'It went ashore after evolving. Its entire body is clad in a sturdy armor.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('22', '1', '0', 0x61726f6e, '0', '9', 0x36, '0', '0', 0x31, '0', '0', '0', '50', 0x3730, 0x313030, '40', '40', '30', '96', 0x3332, '157', '64', '180', '128', '4', '72', 'if ($this->Level() >=32) return \'Lairon\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Sturdy|100|Rock Head|50|Heavy Metal|10', '', 'In order to build up its steel body, it eats iron ore. This pesky Pokémon is known to eat railroad tracks.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('23', '1', '0', 0x6172746963756e6f, '0', '15', 0x33, '0', '0', '0', '0', 0x33, '0', '90', 0x3835, 0x313030, '95', '125', '85', '215', 0x3330, '145', '64', '3', '255', '4', '162', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Pressure|100|Snow Cloak|10', '', 'A legendary bird Pokémon. It can create blizzards by freezing moisture in the air.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('24', '1', '0', 0x617564696e6f, '0', '1', '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '103', 0x3630, 0x3836, '60', '86', '50', '255', 0x3136, '20', '128', '255', '128', '1', '42', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Healer|100|Regenerator|50|Klutz|10', '', 'Using the feelers on its ears, it can tell how someone is feeling or when an egg might hatch.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('25', '1', '0', 0x61786577, '0', '16', '0', '0', 0x31, '0', '0', '0', '0', '46', 0x3837, 0x3630, '30', '40', '57', '64', 0x3130, '1', '64', '75', '128', '4', '82', 'if ($this->Level() >=38) return \'Fraxure\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Rivalry|100|Mold Breaker|50|Unnerve|10', '', 'Its large tusks have a tendency to break, but each time they grow back, they grow in harder and sturdier.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('26', '1', '0', 0x617a656c66, '0', '14', '0', '0', 0x32, '0', '1', '0', '0', '75', 0x313235, 0x3730, '125', '70', '115', '210', '0', '128', '255', '3', '255', '4', '162', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Levitate|100', '', 'When Azelf flew, people gained the determination to do things. It was the birth of willpower.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('27', '1', '0', 0x617a756d6172696c6c, '0', '11', '0', 0x33, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '100', 0x3530, 0x3830, '50', '80', '50', '153', 0x3136, '204', '128', '75', '128', '1', '22', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Thick Fat|100|Huge Power|50|Sap Sipper|10', '', 'Its long ears are superb sensors. It can distinguish the movements of things in water and tell what they are.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('28', '1', '0', 0x617a7572696c6c, '0', '1', '0', 0x31, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '50', 0x3230, 0x3430, '20', '40', '20', '33', 0x32, '139', '128', '150', '191', '1', '22', 'if ($this->Emotion(\'Friendship\') > 128) return \'Marill\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Thick Fat|100|Huge Power|50|Sap Sipper|10', '', 'It swings its large, nutrient-filled tail around to fight opponents bigger than itself.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('29', '1', '0', 0x6261676f6e, '0', '16', '0', '0', 0x31, '0', '0', '0', '0', '45', 0x3735, 0x3630, '40', '30', '50', '89', 0x3232, '184', '64', '45', '128', '4', '82', 'if ($this->Level() >=30) return \'Shelgon\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Rock Head|100|Sheer Force|10', '', 'Dreaming of one day flying, it practices by leaping off cliffs every day.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('30', '1', '0', 0x62616c746f79, '0', '5', 0x3134, '0', '0', '0', '0', 0x31, '0', '40', 0x3430, 0x3535, '40', '70', '55', '58', 0x3132, '196', '128', '255', '255', '2', '42', 'if ($this->Level() >=36) return \'Claydol\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Levitate|100', '', 'Discovered in ancient ruins, it moves by spinning around and forms a group when it finds others.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('31', '1', '0', 0x62616e65747465, '0', '8', '0', '0', 0x32, '0', '0', '0', '0', '64', 0x313135, 0x3635, '83', '63', '65', '179', 0x36, '171', '64', '45', '128', '1', '52', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Insomnia|100|Frisk|50|Cursed Body|10', '', 'A doll that became a Pokémon over its grudge of being thrown away. It seeks the child who disowned it.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('32', '1', '0', 0x626172626f616368, '0', '11', 0x35, 0x31, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '50', 0x3438, 0x3433, '46', '41', '60', '92', 0x32, '255', '128', '190', '128', '2', '42', 'if ($this->Level() >=30) return \'Whiscash\';', '', '', '', '0', '0', 'Oblivious|100|Anticipation|50|Hydration|10', '', 'Its slimy body is hard to grasp. In one region, it is said to have been born from hardened mud.', '', '', '', '', ''),
